title: TTF Cheat Sheet
author: spacew00t
pages:
#- §l<Original Work's Title Here>
----------------§r§oBy <Author's Name>
§r-------------------Transcribed by <Your Name> on <Month> <Date>, <Year in Roman Numerals> at <Your Location>
-------------------§oTBI: <Terminus Book Identifier>
#- §lTerminus Book Identifier
----------------§rWhen you are ready to sign your book, get a TBI from the current Terminus Head Librarians (currently Spacew00t and OogalaBoogala). If they are not online, then leave it blank until you get the TBI.
#- §lMulti-Volume Works
----------------§rWhen signing the book, add v.1 to the end of its title for first volumes, v.2 for second volumes, v.3 for third volumes, and so on.
